Package upo.eps.base

Class CommonPageTest

java.lang.Object
upo.eps.base.BaseTest
upo.eps.base.CommonPageTest
Direct Known Subclasses:
EpsHomePageTest, ExamplePageTest
public abstract class CommonPageTest extends BaseTest
Common test class containing tests that apply to all pages. All page-specific test classes should extend this class to inherit common tests. Common tests include: - Logo presence and visibility - Page load verification - Title verification - Footer presence These tests can be overridden in specific test classes if needed.

    • getLogoLocator

      protected org.openqa.selenium.By getLogoLocator()
      Override this method to provide the logo locator for the specific page. Default locator looks for images with "Logo" in the alt attribute.

    • getFooterLocator

      protected org.openqa.selenium.By getFooterLocator()
      Override this method to provide the footer locator for the specific page. Default locator looks for footer element.

    • getMainMenuLocator

      protected org.openqa.selenium.By getMainMenuLocator()
      Override this to provide the main menu locator for the specific page. Default locator looks for a nav element with class 'main-menu'.
